{"tid":1405562,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"為咗香港，今晚港島集會要和平","createTime":"2019-08-04T10:16:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T12:00:17.000Z","uid":182993,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"61cc2a46e4d94ee2447c8552ca4412ef119ccc0d","tid":1405562,"uid":182993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:16:42.000Z","msg":"大家記住，今晚最好唔好有衝擊，<span style=\"color: maroon;\">我地應該要將目光放係聽日，或者聽日持續嘅罷工行動。</span><br />\n<br />\n我地需要人手進行聽日嘅全港全民不合作運動，今晚諗住衝嘅各位勇武派，不如留一留力，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">聽日早啲起身堵路逼地鐵</span>，直接癱瘓全香港交通，會比你今晚衝有效得多。<br />\n<br />\n如果聽日成功，啫係呢個不合作運動會一直持續落去，逼班廢柴出黎回應/處理，再商討下一步行動。<br />\n<br />\n利申：做過前線，真係好攰<br />\n<br />\n西環見。"},{"pid":"87b2db51d289cdfb3822e38e6abbe9a98e8e75e3","tid":1405562,"uid":182993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:17:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c7361d5d5f90547a6fb2e3bfca5bb551ffe58c7","tid":1405562,"uid":182993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:18:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44691cc4d277d96e9fc4aba4ae6cce4a3a65b153","tid":1405562,"uid":182993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:21:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"783fe92ad34033cd620efdd080c3230668ce5860","tid":1405562,"uid":182993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:25:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4131732158b82546dfdb9da0964edbedf0e726b2","tid":1405562,"uid":182993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:26:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc2aa17a0726786a4fe84f0d55db9f4f20492849","tid":1405562,"uid":182993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:27:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb8c2241705a72075d7d1688c4ff4a46962e8596","tid":1405562,"uid":228955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:31:47.000Z","msg":"等班狗狗上晒裝備然之後冇得發洩 谷住度氣咁收工"},{"pid":"6ec09ca33c8a5d48758342570092151590ee497f","tid":1405562,"uid":182993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"s